### **4. 37_RealTimeChartPanel**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes streaming numeric data in a clean, real-time updating chart layout.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# RealTimeChartPanel - Live Data Visualization Tool

RealTimeChartPanel turns incoming values into a smooth, auto-scrolling chart for dashboards or metric feeds.

## Features
- Real-time line chart  
- Adjustable refresh speed  
- Scrollable history  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/37_RealTimeChartPanel.git
cd 37_RealTimeChartPanel
python visualize.py
